Actions.Text: REFERRED TO CORPORATIONS, AUTHORITIES AND COMMISSIONS

Title: Relates to establishing the green affordable pre-electrification program
Summary: Establishes the green affordable pre-electrification program to assist owners and tenants in residential properties in curing structural and building code defects which render the properties ineligible for climate change adaptation and resiliency project grants.
LawCode: Add ยง1872-b, Pub Auth L
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the public authorities law, in relation to establishing the green affordable pre-electrification program
